setupDB

private void setupDB()
              throws eu.ist.astra.persistency.PersistencyException
Performs the setup of the database model. IMPORTANT: There is not a table for representing Application in the DB model of the client yet. Therefore, we have not established APPLICATION_ID as a foreign key of that table (in the back-end is SharedApplication). If a table for representing Applications in the client DB is created, here APPLICATION_ID SHOULD REFERENCE THIS TABLE AS A FOREIGN KEY IN ORDER TO KEEP INTEGRITY.

Throws:
eu.ist.astra.persistency.PersistencyException
